            <p><span><img src="img/wine_yhq.png"></span><span>优惠券</span><a class="wine_HB_num">1张可用</a><span class="wine_hb" style="float: right;width: 16px;height: 16px;"><img style="width: 100%;" src="img/wine_hbss.png"></span></p>
